Package net.tnemc.core.manager

Class ReceiptManager

java.lang.Object
net.tnemc.core.manager.ReceiptManager
public class ReceiptManager extends Object
Manages receipts for transactions. Provides methods to add, retrieve, and remove receipts by their UUID, time, and within specific time ranges.
Since:
0.1.3.0
Author:
creatorfromhell
